Author: complexmariner
Text: omgg I constantly tell all my friends all this positive shit and try to advocate for body positivity and safe dieting and how to keep a healthy relationship with food,,,, yet still never take the own advice i love to preach

Author: kindbear_kindbud
Text: This is so wholesome :') When my ED first started, my mom was trying to lose a few pounds, and I got really concerned that she did it healthily/ not disordered. Like, her trying to lose weight really triggered me, but I also didn't want her to suffer like I was.
